Terraform Varabels
----------------------
in realtime we will write seperate files for provider,varabels
provider.tf
-----------
provider "aws" {
region = "us-east-1"
}
-------------------------------
resources.tf
-----------
resources "aws_instance" "app"{
tags ={
name = var.iname
env = var.envname
}
ami = var.ami_id
instance_type = var.itype
kay_name = var.key
avilability_zone = var.zone
root_Block_device{
volume_size = var.volume
}
}
