========================================================
but in real time we dont mention default values on varable file
for store varibles we havet to create another filelike

->dev.auto.tfvar
---------------------------------------------------------------
iname= "dev-instance"
envname= "dev"
ami_id= "ami-06067086cf86c58e6"
itype= "t3.micro"
key= "aws"
zone= "us-east-1b"
volume= 20
===================================
to excute
===========
terraform plan -var-file=dev.auto.tfvar
terraform apply -var-file=dev.auto.tfvar
==========================================================================

